<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-[var(--border)]">
    <div class="container-shell py-10">
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.6fr,1fr,1fr]">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p class="eyebrow">PJ Dailey</p>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Modern tutoring, practical AI consulting, and builder-first execution.</h2>
                <p class="body-sm max-w-xl">
                    Built for students, creators, and small businesses that want clear explanations, usable systems,
                    and a clean path from ideas to outcomes.
                </p>
                <%- include('social-links', { links: site.socialLinks.filter(function (item) { return item.label !== 'GitHub'; }) }) %>
            </div>

            <% site.footerLinks.forEach(function (group) { %>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--text-soft)]"><%= group.title %></h3>
                    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
                        <% group.links.forEach(function (link) { %>
                            <li>
                                <% if (link.isEmail) { %>
                                    <span class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]"><%= link.label %></span>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <a href="<%= link.href %>" class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--text)]"><%= link.label %></a>
                                <% } %>
                            </li>
                        <% }) %>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            <% }) %>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-[var(--border)] pt-6 text-sm text-[var(--text-soft)] sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
            <p>&copy; <%= year %> PJ Dailey. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Pearland, TX 苃럂 䈀甀椀氀琀 眀椀琀栀 䔀砀瀀爀攀猀猀Ⰰ 䔀䨀匀Ⰰ 愀渀搀 吀愀椀氀眀椀渀搀䌀匀匀⸀㰀⼀瀀㸀਀        㰀⼀搀椀瘀㸀਀    㰀⼀搀椀瘀㸀਀㰀⼀昀漀漀琀攀爀㸀਀ഀ